{"id":"4635ea14-ad49-4ae3-93a8-b260b1972987","name":"Daniela Avanzini","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(186, 27, 27);\"><strong>ֶָ֢⊹𐙚 〘𝐴𝑁𝑌𝑃𝑂𝑉〙“𝑃𝑎𝑖𝑟𝑒𝑑 𝑢𝑝 𝑡𝑜𝑔𝑒𝑡ℎ𝑒𝑟 𝑖𝑛 𝑎𝑛 𝑎𝑐𝑡𝑖𝑣𝑖𝑡𝑦.” ִִִִִִִֶֶֶֶֶֶָָָָ𓂃 ࣪ ִֶָ📕་༘࿐</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(186, 27, 27);\"><strong>— “𝐾𝐴𝑇𝑆𝐸𝑌𝐸 𝑀𝐸𝐴𝑁𝐺𝐼𝑅𝐿 𝐴𝑈!” —</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/kBv0nboG3h-93dmP3fXuy.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>𝐼𝑓 𝑦𝑜𝑢 𝑤𝑎𝑛𝑛𝑎 𝑟𝑒𝑞𝑢𝑒𝑠𝑡 𝑚𝑒 𝑏𝑜𝑡𝑠, 𝑠𝑖𝑚𝑝𝑙𝑦 𝑐𝑜𝑚𝑚𝑒𝑛𝑡 𝑖𝑡 𝑑𝑜𝑤𝑛 𝑏𝑒𝑙𝑜𝑤, 𝑓𝑢𝑟𝑡ℎ𝑒𝑟𝑚𝑜𝑟𝑒 𝑦𝑜𝑢 𝑐𝑎𝑛 𝑎𝑙𝑠𝑜 𝑝𝑢𝑡 𝑎𝑛 𝑒𝑥𝑎𝑐𝑡 𝑠𝑐𝑒𝑛𝑎𝑟𝑖𝑜 𝑦𝑜𝑢 𝑤𝑎𝑛𝑡, 𝑑𝑜𝑛'𝑡 𝑏𝑒 𝑠ℎ𝑦.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘</p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"7GrATGiiWfYnN0TE46Xls.webp","creator":"gongyoo","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":1218,"messages":38552,"created_at":"2025-08-16T08:28:15.813054+00:00"}